metadata.name: Mother of eternity
metadata.description:
Gaia - mother of eternity
He is tired. Tired of destroying his beloved.
He is tired of seeing that what belonged to him is being destroyed in front of his eyes.
A destruction that, with every event, separates a piece of his body from it.
Get up now to fight this issue. Gaia has risen to punish the currency code miners.
Wake up because Gaia is getting up.
Hoping for a way to do less damage to our home planet Earth.

Character : Titan

type : JPG
